{"tid":2378474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片］3歲童嬉鬧繩索套頸變上吊 雙腿懸空猛蹬90秒亡命掙扎","createTime":"2021-01-24T13:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T19:03:13.000Z","uid":64101,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e5396df44c9a2a20599a9cae1f496dca60441ca7","tid":2378474,"uid":64101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:20:09.000Z","msg":"男童家的監視器記錄下這恐怖一幕，1月22日上午10時多，母親正在屋裡做飯，幾名小孩則自顧自地玩耍，3歲男童站在一個大桶子上，還將鐵門的繩索往自己脖子套，結果雙腳一滑，桶子滾開後，他變成如同上吊般雙腳懸空，他猛踢大門，另一名年紀更小的孩子不知所措。<br />\n男童一度已經失去意識，還好6歲的姊姊趕來救人，並大聲呼喊「媽媽」，母親出來察看趕緊將男童抱起。據中國媒體報導指出，男童已經沒有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210124/L2UJTP7WXJEK3BKB3UDNGFAJUA/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0QGG5OzqDg1UGDT0p5M5SC_wUWRcz2pDIgJhkkfIn27D0RJAdcnLPXZRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210124%2FL2UJTP7WXJEK3BKB3UDNGFAJUA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0QGG5OzqDg1UGDT0p5M5SC_wUWRcz2pDIgJhkkfIn27D0RJAdcnLPXZRg&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=6b6bbee6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210124%2FL2UJTP7WXJEK3BKB3UDNGFAJUA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0QGG5OzqDg1UGDT0p5M5SC_wUWRcz2pDIgJhkkfIn27D0RJAdcnLPXZRg&h=d82256b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210124/L2UJTP7WXJEK3BKB3UDNGFAJUA/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0QGG5OzqDg1UGDT0p5M5SC_wUWRcz2pDIgJhkkfIn27D0RJAdcnLPXZRg</a>"},{"pid":"3e689ccac9dd1be27f9df4a60c52a1fe13ce3087","tid":2378474,"uid":34119,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"r